, t 

ttestfromMeans<-function(x1, x2, sd1, sd2, n1, n2)  
{
df<-n1 + n2 - 2
poolvar<-(((n1-1)*sd1^2)+((n2-1)*sd2^2))/df
t<-(x1-x2)/sqrt(poolvar*((1/n1)+(1/n2)))
sig<-2*(1-(pt(abs(t),df)))
paste("t(df = ", df, ") = ", t, ", p = ", sig, sep = "")
}
